            "failure_message": "Requires shame already elevated, then a noticeable anger spike (not just baseline irritability). Grounds it in negative self-evaluation plus elevated threat/arousal (social heat). Caps contempt/hatred so it stays defensive rather than coldly degrading, and caps agency so it doesn’t read as swaggering dominance. Also caps remorse so a strongly harm-aware state doesn’t unrealistically present as a snapping cover response."
