    "actor_description": "Heat crawls up my neck and I can feel myself shrinking inside my own skin\u2014like I'm being pinned by attention. Then the next thing out of me is sharp: a snap meant to make the moment back up. It\u2019s not courage; it\u2019s cover. I\u2019m trying to stop the looking before it gets under me.",
